{"tid":1756383,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"分化撚  離間撚  煽動撚 白票撚報料舉報清剿區(1)：思覺脫 太skr","createTime":"2019-11-26T04:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T12:19:13.000Z","uid":221265,"like":18,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"66d05aae1e9397cedb84830c2ce8ec3107e31b75","tid":1756383,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oJUQysi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoJUQysi.jpg&h=191bbda0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依啲人經常出啲偽命題post引戰，目的：<br />\n1.分化 內耗<br />\n2.大家花一分鐘時間答佢 同佢爭辨<br />\n就少一分鐘時間做實事<br />\n<br />\n區選完咗  佢哋就會出第二啲話題去離間  分化  抹黑<br />\n一定亦會離間分化抹黑區選裡面贏咗嘅人<br />\n同埋亦會增開不同戰線<br />\n互相猜波做假民意洗版洗post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家舉報<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n睇黎大家都收貨，可以如常慶祝聖誕了！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eBbxbS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eBbxbS</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>又偽命題<br />\n<br />\n根本無人收貨<br />\n得你話</strong>"},{"pid":"8a59243f15c6f7be871e90a5fcf041258f440a5a","tid":1756383,"uid":316537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:20:26.000Z","msg":"一早已經block左"},{"pid":"b533530daee5c6037cbac02545f6e356749701f9","tid":1756383,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a59243f15c6f7be871e90a5fcf041258f440a5a","tid":1756383,"uid":316537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:20:26.000Z","msg":"一早已經block左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:21:56.000Z","msg":"仲有大量<br />\n<br />\n日日夜夜開post 入post <br />\n吊埋晒啲空氣<br />\n<br />\n不斷做fake news去屈依個果個"},{"pid":"a2cbe1c27db443f4f8fe3bd84ec4335dcca35410","tid":1756383,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:24:37.000Z","msg":"大家報料啦<br />\n為民除害"},{"pid":"ccaf862074d89f627cb9144955b43726b7cc5417","tid":1756383,"uid":124616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:25:50.000Z","msg":"搵人follow